[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - New-diagnosis event                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Procedure-scheduled event                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-cluster event                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management-program-enrollment event                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - High-risk-OB enrollment event                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Episode object created]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - episode_id                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - episode_type                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - patient_id                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - episode_start_date                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - expected_episode_end_date (for bounded episodes)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - care_plan_reference                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - active_coordination_tasks                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - episode_protocol_reference                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - episode_relationships (other active episodes)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - active_care_team_members                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - involved_partner_organizations                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: episode object stored; coordination tasks queued; │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    patient onboarding scheduled]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── MULTI-SYSTEM LONGITUDINAL STORE HYDRATION ────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient longitudinal store]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions (problem list)                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active medications (med list across sources)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Allergies                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care plans                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active episodes                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active coordination tasks (referrals, prior auths,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointments, transitions, monitoring tasks)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounters                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent labs and imaging                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient preferences (preferred name, language,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      preferred channels, caregiver context)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver designations and consent scopes               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-determinants context (where captured)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-history flags (where applicable)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent posture (per-partner-organization,              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      per-data-class)                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Multi-system data sources]                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Inpatient EHR (FHIR-native or HL7-v2-translated)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Outpatient EHR (FHIR-native or proprietary-API)         │
