[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    337[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      intimate-partner violence, substance-use crisis):       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    338[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ROUTE TO CRISIS PATHWAY (per recipe 11.8 patterns)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    339[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive disclosures (mandatory-reporting categories): │
