[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    474[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      screen was positive, response routes appropriately)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    475[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    476[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: response cleared for delivery, replaced with a    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    safer template, or regenerated with corrections]          │
