[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ESCALATION ROUTING ───────────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    483[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    484[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Escalation triggers]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    485[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute clinical event detected: 911 or institutional     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      triage workflow                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    487[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis screen positive: per recipe 11.8 patterns        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    488[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stalled referral past institutional threshold:          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    489[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      escalate to human nurse navigator                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    490[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stalled prior-auth past institutional threshold:        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    491[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      escalate to prior-auth team                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    492[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multiple missed appointments: escalate to               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    493[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination team                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    494[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination failure that the assistant cannot          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    495[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      resolve: escalate to human navigator                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    496[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient explicitly requests human                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    497[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Out-of-scope clinical question: escalate to             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    498[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinical team                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive disclosure: escalate to appropriate           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    500[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway                                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver burden disclosure: escalate to social         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      work or care navigation                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-determinants barrier (transportation,            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    504[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      financial, food, housing): escalate to care             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    505[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      navigation                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    506[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    507[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Escalation targets]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - 911 or institutional triage workflow                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis pathway (988, institutional crisis line)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Human nurse navigator                                   │
