[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    580[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool calls with arguments and results                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    581[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generated assistant responses                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    582[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active model and prompt versions                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    583[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active episode-protocol-corpus version                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    584[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active criticality-classifier version                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    585[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    586[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    587[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-specific retention discipline]               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    588[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to longest of HIPAA's six-year          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    589[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      minimum, state-specific medical-record retention        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    590[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      rules, and any litigation-hold obligations              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    591[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-organization shared-data records governed by      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    592[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      data-sharing-agreement retention terms                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    593[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    594[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outcome correlation as long-time-horizon commitment]      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    595[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-quarter to multi-year implementation              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    596[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Owned jointly by care-management leadership,            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    597[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      operations, and data science                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    598[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode-type, per-cohort tracking                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    599[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    600[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry]                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    601[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement rate by patient cohort                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    602[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode-specific engagement                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    603[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-status-update timeliness                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    604[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prior-auth-status-update timeliness                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    605[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stalled-referral identification rate                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    606[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stalled-prior-auth identification rate                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    607[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Escalation rate                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    608[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation-coverage rate                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    609[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    610[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    611[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled clinical-quality review]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    612[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample of escalations,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    613[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      criticality-pathway events, and low-confidence          │
