[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    615[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reviewers tag failure modes (out-of-scope,              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    616[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      stale-data, criticality-miss, criticality-              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    617[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      false-positive, cross-org-data-sharing-violation,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    618[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caregiver-context-violation)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    619[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode-protocol-corpus revisions driven by review      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    620[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      findings                                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    621[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                                  │
