[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    623[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: audit trail, telemetry, learning signals,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    624[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    episode-protocol-corpus-revision proposals]               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    625[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                              │
